description:
&lt;p&gt;Sussex NHS Commissioners is recruiting a GP IT Manager to lead on the delivery of the GP IT Operating Model and associated technical projects. We are looking for an experienced and motivated individual with excellent interpersonal and communication skills to support GP practices with their IT requirements. This will involve working closely with two other GP IT managers, IT Service providers and practices across Sussex.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This is a permanent role that may be based in Worthing, Hove or Lewes.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Please contact Natasha Darby natasha.darby@nhs.net 07909 936852 for an informal discussion about the post.&lt;/p&gt;
